# No Emojis -- Use Icons

- Never use emoji characters (unicode emoji) in source code, comments, documentation, or commit messages.
- When a visual indicator is needed in the UI, use an SVG icon or an icon component instead.
- In Markdown docs (README, etc.), use plain text headings and bullet points -- no emoji prefixes.

